    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>herby Greek cheese mash</strong> on a plate, make a well in the centre and fill with the <strong>harissa lean beef mince ragù</strong></p><p>Crumble over the<strong> remaining Greek cheese </strong>and sprinkle over the<strong> remaining chopped parsley </strong>and<strong> mint</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
